Gelb Consulting Group Inc. is a
Houston, Texas -based strategic marketing consulting firm. Gelb is one of Houston’s largest and experienced strategic marketing firms serving clients globally in a variety of industries including health care, oil and gas, media, manufacturing, and technology. The firm is noted for its long-term relationships, some over 20 years, with such companies as Hines in corporate real estate;
Schlumberger in oil and gas; and M. D. Anderson Cancer Center in healthcare.
